== 运营 ==
Metrorex是布加勒斯特地铁的运营公司，由罗马尼亚运输和基础设施部完全所有，曾有一个合并布加勒斯特地下和地上所有公共交通的计划，但并未实现。

=== 运营時間 ===
布加勒斯特地铁於每天 5 點到23 點間運行，高峰時段1號線和3號線共線段、2號線每3-5分鐘一班，1號線和3號線非共線段6分鐘一班，4號線8分鐘一班；其餘時間，1號線和3號線共線段每5-6分鐘一班、2號線每5-8分鐘一班，1號線和3號線非共線段8-12分鐘一班，4號線9-12分鐘一班。1號線東端的{{Tsl|en|Pantelimon metro station|潘泰利蒙站}}至{{Tsl|en|Republica metro station|共和站 (布加勒斯特地鐵)|共和站}}之間為[[單線鐵路|單線鐵路]]，僅有一半的列車會駛抵潘泰利蒙站，潘泰利蒙站的班距大約18-20分鐘。<ref>{{Cite web|title=METROREX Operation schedule in working days|url=http://www.metrorex.ro/operation_schedule__in_working_days_p787-2|access-date=2022-03-04|work=www.metrorex.ro|language=en|archive-date=2022-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220407202026/http://www.metrorex.ro/operation_schedule__in_working_days_p787-2}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=METROREX Operation schedule in non-working days and holidays|url=http://www.metrorex.ro/operation_schedule__in_non-working_days_and_holidays_p788-2|access-date=2022-03-04|work=www.metrorex.ro|language=en|archive-date=2022-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220304213047/http://www.metrorex.ro/operation_schedule__in_non-working_days_and_holidays_p788-2}}</ref>

=== 票務 ===
布加勒斯特地铁的單程票價格為3[[罗马尼亚列伊|列伊]]，要轉乘其他交通工具，可購買綜合交通卡，價格為5列伊，可搭乘一次地鐵，並在120分鐘內無限制搭乘電車、公交車，一次購買10趟單程票為25列伊，綜合交通卡為45列伊。24與72小時套票價格分別為8、20列伊，24與72小時綜合交通卡價格分別為14、35列伊。定期票有週票至年票不等時常，價格30至700列伊，其中月票價格為80列伊；綜合交通卡定期票價格50至1200列伊，其中月票價格為140列伊。<ref>{{Cite web|title=METROREX Travel Tickets|url=http://www.metrorex.ro/travel_tickets_p1382-2|access-date=2022-03-04|work=www.metrorex.ro|language=en|archive-date=2022-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220228105351/http://www.metrorex.ro/travel_tickets_p1382-2}}</ref>

== 未來計畫 ==

=== 路線延長 ===
據"2016 - 2030 年布加勒斯特地鐵發展戰略"，<ref>{{Cite web|title=Planul de mobilitate urbană durabilă 2016-2030 Regiunea București – Ilfov|url=https://doc.pmb.ro/servicii/transporturi_drumuri/docs/planul_de_mobilitate_durabila_2016-2030.pdf|access-date=2022-03-05|year=2015|format=PDF|pages=322、370|language=ro|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210714194525/https://doc.pmb.ro/servicii/transporturi_drumuri/docs/planul_de_mobilitate_durabila_2016-2030.pdf|archive-date=2021-07-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>布加勒斯特地铁現有線路中2、3、4、5號線均有延長計畫，2號線計畫北延1.6公里、增設兩站，3號線則計畫西延3.7公里、增設4站。另外2號線還計畫在南端向[[貝爾切尼鄉_(伊爾福夫縣)|貝爾切尼]]延長3站<ref>{{Cite web|title=Magistrala de metrou M2 va fi extinsă. Cel puțin 3 stații noi vor fi construite|url=https://www.digi24.ro/stiri/economie/transporturi/magistrala-de-metrou-m2-va-fi-extinsa-cel-putin-3-statii-noi-vor-fi-construite-1731305|access-date=2022-03-05|date=2021-11-10|work=www.digi24.ro|language=ro|archive-date=2022-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220305173603/https://www.digi24.ro/stiri/economie/transporturi/magistrala-de-metrou-m2-va-fi-extinsa-cel-putin-3-statii-noi-vor-fi-construite-1731305}}</ref>。4號線計畫向南延伸，成為第二條南北向貫穿布加勒斯特的地鐵，延伸路線長10.84公里，計畫增設13站，可行性研究已於2020年11月公布<ref>{{Cite web|title=Proiectul privind construcţia unei noi linii de metrou în Capitală, de la Gara de Nord la Gara Progresul, în consultare publică|url=https://adevarul.ro/news/bucuresti/proiectul-privind-constructia-linii-metrou-capitala-gara-nord-gara-progresul-consultare-publica-1_60f80e585163ec42714d0a8e/index.html|access-date=2022-03-05|date=2021-07-21|work=adevarul.ro|language=ro|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210721182702/https://adevarul.ro/news/bucuresti/proiectul-privind-constructia-linii-metrou-capitala-gara-nord-gara-progresul-consultare-publica-1_60f80e585163ec42714d0a8e/index.html|archive-date=2021-07-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>。5號線則計畫向東延伸，5號線被分為數階段建造，最初通車的為{{Tsl|en|Eroilor metro station|厄洛勒站}}以西的一期路段，二期路段自厄洛勒站至{{Tsl|ro|Piața Iancului metro station|皮亞薩·揚庫魯伊站}}，長約5.4公里，有6個車站，計畫2025年建成，三期將繼續東延至潘泰利蒙站，但時程未定，預計2032年以後才有可能建成。<ref>{{Cite web|title=In ce stadiu este proiectul metroului pana la Pantelimon si cand ar putea fi gata?|url=https://www.wall-street.ro/articol/Auto/237846/in-ce-stadiu-este-proiectul-metroului-pana-la-pantelimon-si-cand-ar-putea-fi-gata.html|access-date=2022-03-05|date=2019-01-10|work=Wall-Street|language=ro|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190111021842/https://www.wall-street.ro/articol/Auto/237846/in-ce-stadiu-este-proiectul-metroului-pana-la-pantelimon-si-cand-ar-putea-fi-gata.html|archive-date=2019-01-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 新路線 ===
布加勒斯特計畫建造新的6號線連結{{Tsl|en|Gara de Nord metro station|北站 (布加勒斯特地鐵)|北站}}與[[布加勒斯特亨利·科安德国际机场|布加勒斯特亨利·科安德国际机场]]，路線總長14.2公里，設12個車站。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Metrorex: Metroul din Drumul Taberei va circula de la mijlocul anului viitor. Când vor începe lucrările la linia de metrou Otopeni|url=https://www.mediafax.ro/social/metrorex-metroul-din-drumul-taberei-va-circula-de-la-mijlocul-anului-viitor-cand-vor-incepe-lucrarile-la-linia-de-metrou-otopeni-15751045|access-date=2022-03-21|date=2016-09-29|work=Mediafax.ro|language=ro|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210515062546/https://www.mediafax.ro/social/metrorex-metroul-din-drumul-taberei-va-circula-de-la-mijlocul-anului-viitor-cand-vor-incepe-lucrarile-la-linia-de-metrou-otopeni-15751045|archive-date=2021-05-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>2019 年初[[欧洲联盟|歐盟]]宣布暫時只為該線路的前半提供資金<ref>{{Cite web|title=Comisia Europeană a aprobat finanțarea pentru jumătate din magistrala de metrou M6. Corina Crețu: Sper ca autoritățile române să găsească soluții pentru finalizarea magistralei, ca să se poată circula până la Aeroportul Otopeni|url=https://monitorizari.hotnews.ro/stiri-infrastructura_articole-22971639-comisia-europeana-aprobat-finantarea-pentru-jumatate-din-magistrala-metrou-m6-corina-cretu-sper-autoritatile-romane-gaseasca-solutii-pentru-finalizarea-magistralei-poata-circula-pana-aeroportul-otopen.htm|access-date=2022-03-21|date=2019-02-13|work=monitorizari.hotnews.ro|language=ro|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201206005438/https://monitorizari.hotnews.ro/stiri-infrastructura_articole-22971639-comisia-europeana-aprobat-finantarea-pentru-jumatate-din-magistrala-metrou-m6-corina-cretu-sper-autoritatile-romane-gaseasca-solutii-pentru-finalizarea-magistralei-poata-circula-pana-aeroportul-otopen.htm|archive-date=2020-12-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>，另外羅馬尼亞交通部還計畫建設一條與6號線平行的鐵路，只設置4個車站，提供機場與市區的快速連結<ref>{{Cite web|title=VIDEO Legătura Capitalei cu Aeroportul Otopeni: De ce se justifică Magistrala 6 de metrou care va costa un miliard de euro, dacă se face și tren direct de zece ori mai ieftin?|url=https://economie.hotnews.ro/stiri-bani_europeni-22785905-euroimpact-legatura-capitalei-aeroportul-otopeni-justifica-magistrala-6-metrou-care-costa-un-miliard-euro-daca-facem-tren-direct-de-zece-ori-mai-ieftin.htm|access-date=2022-03-21|date=2018-10-30|work=economie.hotnews.ro|language=ro|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210620103858/https://economie.hotnews.ro/stiri-bani_europeni-22785905-euroimpact-legatura-capitalei-aeroportul-otopeni-justifica-magistrala-6-metrou-care-costa-un-miliard-euro-daca-facem-tren-direct-de-zece-ori-mai-ieftin.htm|archive-date=2021-06-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>。布加勒斯特地鐵的遠期規劃中還包括東北-西南走向的7號線，以及南側半環線 (8號線)。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Planurile unui metrou pentru nepotii nepotilor: Magistrala M8 Crangasi - Dristor|url=https://www.wall-street.ro/articol/Social/241626/magistrala-m8-crangasi-dristor-ar-avea-17-kilometri-lungime-si-ar-costa-1-8-milioane-de-euro.html|access-date=2022-03-21|date=2019-06-06|work=Wall-Street|language=ro|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190609015207/https://www.wall-street.ro/articol/Social/241626/magistrala-m8-crangasi-dristor-ar-avea-17-kilometri-lungime-si-ar-costa-1-8-milioane-de-euro.html|archive-date=2019-06-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>

